%F A395804 Equals (5/6)*(cot(Pi/20) + cot(Pi/10))*sqrt(1 - sec(Pi/20)^2/4) = (5/6)*(A019979 + A019970)*sqrt(1 - sec(Pi/20)^2/4).
%F A395804 Equals (5/6)*sqrt(2*sqrt(650 + 290*sqrt(5)) - 2*sqrt(5) - 2).
%F A395804 Equals the largest real root of 6561*x^8 + 36450*x^6 - 16503750*x^4 + 55968750*x^2 + 390625.
%e A395804 6.7492878755469948622105348685306452318593883575293...
